<%
// Ophir Service Area
%>

<!-- Page Header -->
<section class="page-header" style="background-image: url('/images/ophir-header.jpg');">
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Tree Service in Ophir, OR</h1>
        <p>Professional Tree Removal, Tree Trimming & Fire Reduction</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Main Content -->
<section class="area-content section-padding">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Intro with Image -->
        <div class="service-intro">
            <div class="intro-text">
                <p>JT & Sons Tree Service LLC proudly provides reliable tree services in Ophir, OR and nearby areas along the Southern Oregon Coast. With over 30 years of experience, our family-owned company offers professional tree removal, tree trimming, stump grinding, emergency services, and fire reduction for residential and commercial properties.</p>
                <p>Ophir's coastal environment and forested landscapes mean properties often have large trees that require professional maintenance. Our experienced crew provides safe and efficient tree care, helping homeowners protect their property and maintain healthy trees.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="intro-image">
                <img src="/images/fire-reduction.jpg" alt="Ophir Tree Service" class="rounded-image">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Services List -->
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>Our Tree Services in Ophir, OR</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Tree Removal</li>
                <li>Tree Trimming</li>
                <li>Stump Grinding</li>
                <li>Emergency Tree Services</li>
                <li>View Clearing & Fire Reduction</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you're searching for professional tree service in Ophir OR, JT & Sons Tree Service LLC provides dependable and affordable tree care.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Info -->
        <div class="contact-info-box">
            <h3>Call today for a free estimate</h3>
            <p>
                <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i> Office: <a href="tel:<%= sitePhone %>"><%= sitePhone %></a><br>
                <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> Cell/Text: <a href="tel:<%= siteCell %>"><%= siteCell %></a><br>
                <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email: <a href="mailto:<%= siteEmail %>"><%= siteEmail %></a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>